The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning method for autonomous driving, which involves training feedforward controllers using offline training on sophisticated models and online evaluation of the controller. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY).
